125
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:49,780
I want to know

126
00:10:51,090 --> 00:10:52,730
what kind of person

127
00:10:53,830 --> 00:10:54,810
made you,

128
00:10:54,990 --> 00:10:57,230
Blood-handed Asura,

129
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:58,550
