00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:07,570
[Lu Tang Birthday Poetry Meeting]

155
00:13:07,230 --> 00:13:08,300
Clear Dew Sorrow?

156
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:09,630
Wasn't that Nan Yan's mother's

157
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,890
