193
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:26,100
I see.

194
00:14:26,430 --> 00:14:27,790
Congratulations.

195
00:14:28,570 --> 00:14:38,500
[Lu Tang Birthday Poetry Meeting]

196
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,060
Please.

