00:17:13,329 --> 00:17:15,920
[Lu Tang Birthday Poetry Meeting]

263
00:17:13,790 --> 00:17:14,550
Great.

264
00:17:14,589 --> 00:17:15,250
Again!

265
00:17:17,829 --> 00:17:20,390
